{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"CodeEditSourceEditor"}],"title":"GutterView","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"GutterView","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"c:@M@CodeEditSourceEditor@objc(cs)GutterView","symbolKind":"class","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"GutterView"}]},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/codeeditsourceeditor.CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor"]]},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/codeeditsourceeditor.CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterView"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/codeeditsourceeditor.CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/CodeEditSourceEditor","doc:\/\/codeeditsourceeditor.CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/TextViewController"],"generated":true,"title":"Text View","anchor":"Text-View"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute","preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"GutterView"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If the gutter needs more space (when the number of digits in the numbers increases eg. adding a line after line 99),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"it will notify it’s delegate via the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/codeeditsourceeditor.CodeEditSourceEditor\/documentation\/CodeEditSourceEditor\/GutterViewDelegate\/gutterViewWidthDidUpdate(newWidth:)"},{"text":" method. In","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoi